{"tid":1067241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3月19日：亞太鐵路會議，由MTR工程師主講","createTime":"2019-03-18T11:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T03:03:34.000Z","uid":202464,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"796f69d340581304536a58381c8b368878e2452c","tid":1067241,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.giievent.tw/terr654982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.giievent.tw%2Fterr654982%2F&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=c80c7bfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.giievent.tw/terr654982/</a><br />\nAsia Pacific Rail 2019<br />\n-亞太鐵路會議：2019年-<br />\n日期：2019年3月19-20日<br />\n地點：香港，Hong Kong Convention &amp; Exhibition Centre<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞太鐵路大會最矚目的當屬港鐵項目經理（訊號）羅志沖及前總訊號工程師（車務）王惠明將主講「更換訊號系統：最佳實踐（Resignalling: best practices）」研討會，內容討論點如何將更換系統時對服務影響減到最少、大規模更換系統時要避開嘅陷阱等等。"},{"pid":"9d5884f3b3b7b7c6ff23ee991420de832285e04a","tid":1067241,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":51,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"c809303d1b943dc6fa0da4411abf456bcaeb4da2","tid":1067241,"uid":192190,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"各位與會者,前日呢次事故 原本起碼會死全港三成人口<br />\n全靠我地努力不懈, 所以結果只係損失兩列列車<br />\n不管你信不信, 反正我話ok就ok　"},{"pid":"7956401afdffeddbebdc215aa93f53d8cc68edd6","tid":1067241,"uid":55924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n幾日前我地模擬左一次列車追尾黎測試列車質素同應變機制 ！<br />\n顯示出港鐵有世界一流既技術！"},{"pid":"50d6024cd64f4814a10719ca975bc3d50abe0558","tid":1067241,"uid":54337,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"Hi.<br />\nWe just crash.<br />\nSo students go to school by bus.<br />\nSor.<br />\nBye."},{"pid":"f887bba520ffa34e1cca38770974c9ea099c4361","tid":1067241,"uid":18948,"like":9